OAISIS DAO has officially launched on Story Protocol!

1. Who are we? @osdotfun

We are a DAO experimenting with the convergence of AI, Crypto, and IP.

2. Our First Product: @storydotfun

At its core, https://t.co/RoQI9Gt4ss is an AI Agent Launchpad + DEX. You can think of it as @virtuals_io + @Uniswap, combined with a token sale mechanism similar to @pumpdotfun + @daosdotfun.

Our key features are as follows:
- No-Code AI Agent Launch
- Smarter AI Agents
- Generating Revenue for AI Agents Through IP
- Contributor Round
- Automatic Buy-Back & Burn
- Permanent Liquidity Lock with Fee Collection
- Dynamic Fee Model

3. Our Token: $OS

The token of this DAO is $OS, and all value accrual within the ecosystem built by the DAO will be concentrated in $OS.

The $OS will be launched on https://t.co/RoQI9Gt4ss in a few weeks, with the bonding curve sale executed in $IP.

4. $OS Contributor Round

The WL (Whitelist) will be distributed among three groups, aiming to enhance DAO recognition and activate the community:

1Ô∏è‚É£ Ossy Friends: Become an Ossy Friend by gathering 10,000 ·¶† points üëâ https://t.co/ZABq8QFuaL
2Ô∏è‚É£ DAO Ambassador: Apply to be an OAISIS Ambassador üëâ https://t.co/FiAtaVW3g2
3Ô∏è‚É£ DAO Core Contributor: Join as a Core Contributor (Dev/Design/Partnership/Marketing) üëâ https://t.co/47PXn2gdZw

5. Join Official Discord! https://t.co/rFpqJi9dmx

Our official Discord is now open‚Äîjoin the community, get your role, and help us build the future together on Story Protocol.

If you want to dive deeper, learn more from the full article here üëâ https://t.co/OfEInqZR3Y

Let's build together!

It‚Äôs time for agent platforms to level-up

Focusing on # of agent launches is kinda mid & not a sustainable revenue source long-term.

Quality of agents *needs* to trump quantity for this sector to make it. 

Think teams know this tho, 

I see @virtuals_io working in the agent-2-agent commerce & comms layer.

I see @arcdotfun putting value on *quality* of agents through curated launches (handshakes)

Agent verticalization going to be important.

- team like Tank, Soulgraph playing with voice and computer use functionality.

& sooo many more.
